Product.name: Light Army Rust Shadow Patina
Product.usHtsDescription: Men Leather Sport HT Shoe EAR99 NLR
Product.title: Jordan 1 Retro High Light Army Rust Shadow Patina
Product.description:
The Air Jordan 1 made its return since the University Blue release in early March of 2021. Despite the release being closer to spring of that year, which usually calls for pastels, the Air Jordan 1 Patina colorway delivers a new way to embrace the season.

The Air Jordan 1 Patina looks as though it was inspired by metal. The backend of the sneaker features grey suede from the collar to the heel. Moving closer to the toe, a mix of copper and black leathers appear. Lastly, a mint Nike Air logo on the tongue is stitched atop a black nylon tongue, bringing a hit of brightness to the otherwise dark colorway.

The Air Jordan 1 Patina released in March of 2021 at select stockists for $170.
